      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ASTON BUGSY (1) rocketed out of the boxes with a strong early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when third (30.40) at The Meadows over 525m. Boasts three wins from three starts out of this box. Key chance in this line up. REAPER (2) doesn't show much early dash but winds into his races, two back missing the frame but last time hitting the line hard to place when third (26.05) in a Mix 3/4 at Warragul last time. Solid record at the distance winning 11 races. Can measure up. DR. BABETTE (4) hit the frame latest (29.85) when third at Sandown in a Grade 5. Has two wins already from this draw. Looks a key chance on best figures. DR. LEVIATE (3) generally performs well over this distance.",
